#: ../source/reference/command/replSetMaintenance.txt:18
msgid ""
"The :dbcommand:`replSetMaintenance` admin command enables or disables the"
" maintenance mode for a :term:`secondary` member of a :term:`replica "
"set`."
msgstr ""

